How customer reviews and ratings work

Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

Sandor Clegane
5.0 out of 5 stars There are Three Reasons You Will Order This. Know What they Are?
Reviewed in the United States on January 2, 2023
Verified Purchase
Interested in ordering this set? I'll give you three simple reasons.

1. A deck by itself costs $10 on Amazon. With this, you get a deck plus 20 tablets for $7.25 (when on sale).

2. Print quality of everything is good.

3. Includes one bonus "tablet" card that contains the phrases sung.

Any negatives about this set? Nothing so big that I'd take a star off the rating. The print of the words for the "songs" for each card on the main reference tablet card is kind of small. So if you don't wear glasses, you might have to squint. And there's no "box" like a traditional set of playing cards would normally come in. So once you take the cards out of the plastic packaging, you need to keep them in the main plastic bag.Having them in a box would have made the set perfect.

Overall, you can't beat what you're getting for the price. Great way to enjoy a classic game with friends and family. And for an unbeatable price.

Reviewed in the United States on December 7, 2023
Verified Purchase

 I like the fact that this is an original game and not some cheap flimsy off brand version. The playing cards are durable as well as the playing cards. Everything is written clear and very easy to read. I always like how this game comes with like a key information card that gives you a little history information about each picture. This is a game that my family, friends, and I have played for many years whether your a small child or an adult it is always fun for holiday get togethers, birthday parties, drinking (for adults of course), or just some fun friend or family nights together. It’s just brings you close together without the use of screens and distractions. We even always bet money like quarters or dollars when playing which makes for more fun and competition. Every time we play it’s lots of laughs, cheering, joking. Just a wholesome tradition full of fun. I would suggest this game for anyone. Even people who have never played. It’s easy to learn.
